-675241736.text: "Many genes in each group are established NRF2 target genes, and included NQO1 and GCLM mRNAs (consistent with our qRT-PCR results) and other known NRF2 targets such as MAFG XREF_BIBR, KEAP1 XREF_BIBR, GSR XREF_BIBR, EPHX1 XREF_BIBR, TXNRD1 XREF_BIBR, PRDX1 XREF_BIBR and TXN XREF_BIBR, all of which were induced in response to L-SUL treatment in both PD and Control hONS cultures."
